y.module.io
Class GIFOutput

java.lang.Object
  y.module.YModule
      y.module.io.IOHandlerModule
          y.module.io.ImageOutputModule
              y.module.io.GIFOutput

public class GIFOutput
extends ImageOutputModule

Exports a diagram to a GIF image. This module provides an option dialog that offers the possibility to modify the settings interactively. Configurable options are the viewport settings, background transparency and tiling.
